blueprint_book.label: Unholy Railbook (v0.1)
blueprint_book.description:
This rail system contains the unholy union of LHD and RHD.  For horitzontal tracks , the top two tracks are LHD and the bottom two are RHD.  For vertical tracks, the left tracks are LHD.

Do not use if you want: 
* Sanity / Elegance / Purpose in life / Peak performance

Do use if you want: 
* Godlessness / Pain and suffering / To watch the world burn / To wake up and choose violence / Peak performance

Warning:  
* The usage of this blueprint book may result in an instaban from servers.
